<body>
    <h1>Akilles App Support</h1>
    
    <p>Akilles is designed for simplicity and efficiency.</p>
    
    <h2>How to:</h2>
    <ol>
        <li>On the Exercise tab:
            <ol type="a">
                <li>Start by adding your favorite exercises.</li>
            </ol>
        </li>
        <li>On the workout tab:
            <ol type="a">
                <li>Build a workout routine with the exercises you have created. Add sets of your exercises that will be completed in the workout.</li>
                <li>Once created, your workouts can be easily reused and modified to fit your progression.</li>
                <li>After each session, easily record your completed sets.</li>
            </ol>
        </li>
        <li>On the daily sets tab:
            <ol type="a">
                <li>Track your daily progress and stay on top of your gains.</li>
            </ol>
        </li>
    </ol>

    <h2>Key Features:</h2>
    
    <h3>Exercise Tracking:</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Log exercise sets with weight, reps, and duration</li>
        <li>View your progress over time with detailed charts</li>
        <li>Track personal records (PRs) for each exercise</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Workout Templates:</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Create custom workout routines</li>
        <li>Easily track multiple exercises in a single session</li>
        <li>Set target weights and reps for each exercise</li>
        <li>Time your sets as needed</li>
        <li>Time your full workout as needed</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Daily Workout Log:</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Record and review your daily exercises</li>
        <li>Review your training history by date</li>
        <li>Analyze your workout data with insightful summaries</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Performance Metrics:</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Monitor rep counts, average weights, and volume load</li>
        <li>Track improvements with percentage changes from 30-day averages</li>
        <li>View max reps, max weight, and best set duration for each exercise</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Categories:</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Organize exercises by muscle groups and categories</li>
        <li>Filter exercises for easy access during workouts</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Detailed Analysis:</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Access statistics for each exercise</li>
        <li>View total workout volume load</li>
        <li>Track progress across different muscle groups</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>User-Friendly Design:</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Intuitive design for quick and easy logging</li>
        <li>Track the exercises that matter to you</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Data Persistence:</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Store your workout data on your device</li>
        <li>Sync across your devices with iCloud integration</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Stopwatch:</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Included to quickly time exercise sets</li>
        <li>Screen does not shut off when timer is active</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you need further assistance, have any questions, would like to recommend additional functionality, or report bugs, please contact us at: akilles.app@gmail.com</p>
